rows.label: tev041401_MSG0007
rows.name: I live in capsule pod Ma-non give me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0008
rows.name:
It is nice. I can set own temperature.
Or have food delivered with press of button.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0009
rows.name:
But Ma-non pod is small. Only one Prone can fit.
I cannot live with my family.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0010
rows.name:
In my old life, whole family slept in large tent.
Me. Little sister. Big sister. Many other kin as well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0011
rows.name:
Sometimes I am lonely sleeping alone.
Sometimes I want to cry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0001
rows.name:
Ugh! Grandfather Auld has one-track mind.
All he talks about is marriage and family.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0002
rows.name: He should worry about his own problems.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0003
rows.name:
Do Earth aliens also get pestered by family?
Does family insist you find worthy mate?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0004
rows.name:
Prone consider it mission to start families early.
Then children learn to be warriors.
Eventually become leaders of own clans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0005
rows.name:
Unmarried Prone of my age is frowned upon.
Relatives say unpleasant things behind back.
...Or sometimes to face.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0006
rows.name:
So wearisome! I do have eyes on mate at moment.
But I cannot rush into anything.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG1001
rows.name: I decided to join BLADE![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG1002
rows.name:
You cannot keep whole city safe by yourself.
It is not right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG1003
rows.name:
But when I asked, BLADE man said I needed to train.
Also that I had to learn "front ear nav."
What is this "front ear nav"? And what is "studying"?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG1004
rows.name: Can I not simply offer grex meat as tribute?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG1005
rows.name:
Yes! I should try this! I will bring great helpings of
grex meat right to BLADE Tower![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0101
rows.name: Thank you for making my wedding possible![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0102
rows.name: Me and Heptana have been hunting across Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0103
rows.name:
Other day, we were chased by massive grex.
But we tricked beast. Sent it tumbling into ravine. Ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0104
rows.name: I could not have done so without brave Heptana.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0105
rows.name:
She makes me want to be better hunter.
She makes me want to protect clan![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0201
rows.name: Enneana knitted us matching sleep-clothes![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0202
rows.name:
She has me wearing sleep-clothes every night.
...I think I like it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0203
rows.name:
Only problem is Enneana's beauty.
I cannot sleep next to her! I can only stare...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0204
rows.name: See bags under eyes? They are bags of happiness.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0205
rows.name: Enneana inspires me to become mighty Prone![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0206
rows.name:
Soon I will be strong enough to vanquish entire gang
of Ganglion![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG3001
rows.name:
Your fight with Ganglion is almost done.
But I will not sit by![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG3002
rows.name:
I hurl fresh grex carcass at BLADE Tower daily.
It is tribute so I can join you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG3003
rows.name: But Earth aliens at BLADE Tower seem angry...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG3004
rows.name: Is tribute of meat not considered sign of readiness?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG3005
rows.name:
...What? I must learn how to use "front ear nav"?
Is that kind of hunting spear?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0301
rows.name: Grandfather Auld once gave me wisdom...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0302
rows.name:
He said greatest pride was not killing beast.
Nor was it victory over Cavern Clan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0303
rows.name:
He said greatest pride was building fine family.
I also appreciate my family.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0304
rows.name:
Little sister, Liana, needs to learn respect.
But still she cared for Grandfather more than anyone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0305
rows.name:
Big sister, Duna, still tries to mother me.
Even though I am married.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0306
rows.name:
And mate Heptana is always by my side.
My family is larger than ever![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0307
rows.name: Now I see how important Grandfather's words are.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0308
rows.name: Family is bastion of strength for all![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG0406
rows.name:
And mate Enneana is always by my side.
My family is larger than ever![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG3010
rows.name:
I hurl many grex carcasses at BLADE Tower as sign
of tribute.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG3011
rows.name:
I want them to make me BLADE so I can protect
city and family.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG3012
rows.name:
Finally, muscular BLADE came over to me.
Said he "liked my moxie."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG3013
rows.name: Then muscleman agreed to make me trainee![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev041401_MSG3014
rows.name:
When I complete training, I will be true BLADE.
Then we will defend city together![ST:wait ]
